name: Renee
what_you_do: J.Renee is an entrepreneur, author, coach, speaker, and faith-driven strategist who empowers women of faith to shatter glass ceilings, break through limitations, and maximize their potential in both life and business using strategy, confidence, and fearless faith.
who_you_serve: J.Renee serves a wide range of organizations and events, including corporations, women's leadership programs, faith-based communities, colleges and universities, and entrepreneurial events.
social_proof: J.Renee has spoken on stages across the country and internationally, including universities, organizations, and events.
business_focus: Empowering women of faith to maximize their potential in life and business.
